platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.ta.k: 從悲傷成長，助少女走出陰霾
美しい色彩の幻想的な旅路
穿梭絢彩世界 探索失落與成長

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: A hopeful girl strives to cope with loss and overcome grief in the imaginative GRIS. This cinematic adventure’s gorgeous design, wonderfully fluid controls, and soothing soundtrack draw you into its memorable world—and keep you there. Face your fears and jump in.
